{"tid":2454034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜與 BNO 家庭視像會面　指英國全國對港人來英感自豪","createTime":"2021-03-20T02:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T03:12:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c46192b2f636ac65b2d1fbeb51112be7312d98","tid":2454034,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"首相府表示，約翰遜於周五下午（19 日）與 4 個新來英的香港 BNO 家庭進行視像會談，該 4 個家庭都是在去年港版國安法實施後，去年來到英國，現已在英國開始生活和工作，會面中，他們與約翰遜討論離開香港的原因和來到英國後的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在會談時表示，對 4 個家庭來到英國，英國全國都感到高興和自豪，又指相信英國會令他們感覺如家一樣。約翰遜說，英國長年擁抱在出生地被剝奪權利和自由，因而轉而來到英國追尋的人。約翰遜又表示，對英國提供 BNO 簽證 5+1 定居計劃感到自豪。<br />\n<br />\nBNO 簽證至今收 2.7 萬申請<br />\n<br />\n首相府透露，自 BNO 簽證於 1 月底開始接受申請以來，英國政府至今收到 2.7 萬個申請。首相府指，BNO 簽證計劃反映英國向港人履行了歷史和道德責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/krishk/status/1372935050015178756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkrishk%2Fstatus%2F1372935050015178756&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2d6a3cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkrishk%2Fstatus%2F1372935050015178756&h=55dac182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/krishk/status/1372935050015178756</a><br />\n<br />\n有份協助安排今次會面的慈善團體領袖 Krish Kandiah 於 Twitter 表示，4 個家庭與約翰遜會面時均感到高興，又透露會面談及醫生、建築師和老師專業資格銜接時遇到的困難，為小孩找學校的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E8%88%87-bno-%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2-%E6%8C%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BE%86%E8%8B%B1%E6%84%9F%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%25BF%25B0%25E9%2581%259C%25E8%2588%2587-bno-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B1%25AA%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=eff2da01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%25BF%25B0%25E9%2581%259C%25E8%2588%2587-bno-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B1%25AA%2F&h=98c1ad4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E8%88%87-bno-%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2-%E6%8C%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BE%86%E8%8B%B1%E6%84%9F%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/prime-minister-meets-hong-kong-bno-families-who-have-come-to-the-uk-19-march-2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fprime-minister-meets-hong-kong-bno-families-who-have-come-to-the-uk-19-march-2021&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=9211690f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/prime-minister-meets-hong-kong-bno-families-who-have-come-to-the-uk-19-march-2021</a>"},{"pid":"7b7be9fe8a775adbd2d8afa7104750fcbaf50e28","tid":2454034,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"&hellip;good"},{"pid":"9d59508ef3bb19d1594a0c99c314a217a744e447","tid":2454034,"uid":375068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:12:24.000Z","msg":"We are the champion my friend~!"}]}